name: Titanium.XML.Notation
summary: Represents a notation declared in the DTD. Implements the DOM Level 2 API on Android and iOS.

properties.name: publicId
properties.summary: The public identifier of this notation. If the public identifier was not specified, this is null.

properties.name: systemId
properties.summary: The system identifier of this notation. If the system identifier was not specified, this is null.
